        <div class="section-title">
            <h2>Hotel Services</h2>
            <p>We offer a wide range of services designed to make your stay memorable and comfortable.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="services-container">
            <div class="service-card">
                <div class="service-icon"><i class="fas fa-utensils"></i></div>
                <h3>Fine Dining</h3>
                <p>Experience culinary excellence at our award-winning restaurants with world-class chefs.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="service-card">
                <div class="service-icon"><i class="fas fa-spa"></i></div>
                <h3>Spa & Wellness</h3>
                <p>Rejuvenate your mind and body with our luxurious spa treatments and wellness programs.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="service-card">
                <div class="service-icon"><i class="fas fa-swimming-pool"></i></div>
                <h3>Infinity Pool</h3>
                <p>Relax by our stunning infinity pool with breathtaking views of the city skyline.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="service-card">
                <div class="service-icon"><i class="fas fa-dumbbell"></i></div>
                <h3>Fitness Center</h3>
                <p>Stay active with our state-of-the-art fitness equipment and personal training sessions.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="service-card">
                <div class="service-icon"><i class="fas fa-concierge-bell"></i></div>
                <h3>Concierge Service</h3>
                <p>Our dedicated concierge team is available 24/7 to assist with all your needs.</p>
