                    "Our stay at Azure Heights was absolutely magnificent. The attention to detail, exceptional service, and luxurious amenities made this our best hotel experience ever. We will definitely be returning!"
                </div>
                <div class="guest-info">
                    <div class="guest-avatar">
                        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1494790108755-2616b786d4d9?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D&auto=format&fit=crop&w=100&q=80" alt="Guest">
